annotation_gdc_id: Id assigned by the GDC to the annotation
annotation_submitter_id: Id assigned to the annotation by the TCGA
case_gdc_id: Id assigned by the GDC to the case
program_name: The program name, e.g. 'TCGA' (the only program with annotations)
endpoint_type: Which type of GDC Annotation API was used, either legacy or current
category: Annotation category name, e.g. 'Acceptable treatment for TCGA tumor'.
entity_barcode: The TCGA barcode that the annottion is associated with
entity_gdc_id: Id assigned by the GDC to the entity
